Located at 15 Richard Street Hindmarsh is an exceptional example of boutique office accommodation.

Comprising 168sqm it contains an open plan work space with central coffee/kitchen area and mezzanine space. Tonnes of natural light throughout plus polished concrete flooring that blends together to create a terrific working environment.

7 on-site car parks are available where are included in the rental.

Rent Reviews: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable

Located 500 metres from the Adelaide Entertainment Centre is 184 Port Road, Hindmarsh. Comprising 488 sqm over 2 levels, the property offers the opportunity for groups to occupy their own building in close proximity to the CBD.

The fitout provides a mix of exposed bricks and commercial gyprock finishes with the configuration being a combination of offices and open plan space plus its own balcony

Prominent signage opportunities are available to traffic coming out of the CBD.

On-site parking plus easy on-street parking available in close proximity.

Lease Term: Negotiable
Rent Reviews: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable
Available: Immediately.
